\label{eq:loss}
\end{equation}

We split the 10,000 test images into a 5,000-image
\emph{sensitivity set} (used for computing the sensitivity matrix
$\mat{S}$ and monitoring per-class accuracy during optimization) and
a 5,000-image \emph{held-out evaluation set} (used only for final
reporting). All accuracy figures reported in the results are measured
on the held-out set unless otherwise noted.

